OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain continuing into
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight, though
OL,8,Fthese will ease somewhat, with some
OL,9,Fclear spells developing across the
OL,10,Feast of the country. Remaining rather
OL,11,Fbreezy, especially across England and
OL,12,FWales, and mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FRemaining breezy on Thursday
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells and showers, however
OL,16,Fthese merging at times to give longer
OL,17,Fspells of rain, and possibly the odd
OL,18,Frumble of thunder. Near normal
OL,19,Ftemperatures.
